# Theme Protection Guidelines

## ğŸ¯ Core Principle

**All theme styling must be centralized or use pre-styled components.** This prevents accidental loss during refactors, merges, or code updates.

## âœ… Always Use

### 1. Pre-Styled Components (Preferred)
```tsx
